{"tid":1427794,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵制精品]跟unlike之後，第二波對精品升級行動！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:44:01.000Z","uid":1670,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed579e8348799fa667aca5ea9c094381c8c2c41","tid":1427794,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"召集所有玩具撚！一齊unlike精品page！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425240\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425240</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟unlike行動之後<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊撕咗手上嘅精品實體單，實體單就係你手上，話撕就撕！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/154324_67eedd52c924832ab45246d7617d6d27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F154324_67eedd52c924832ab45246d7617d6d27.png&h=66dc0873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我本人電子單居多，撕完實體單就諗方法點處理電子單，當然最簡單係就咁咁唔找數，但完全毀滅張單就係同精品，以至同成個玩具業界表態<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撐警撚嘅下場就係咁，人格有問題嘅舖頭永不錄用</span>"},{"pid":"88896f0d05be37b3762eaa14cae084d09dd4ba45","tid":1427794,"uid":8192,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"梗係拎住啲單叫佢退訂先啦"},{"pid":"1159efdf2b585fc678ebdff22797c56d6f8014cc","tid":1427794,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88896f0d05be37b3762eaa14cae084d09dd4ba45","tid":1427794,"uid":8192,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"梗係拎住啲單叫佢退訂先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"亦可，只要係毀滅訂單，斷絕佢收入就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b38b0f95228201141904d8f07dcee1cc25c7a3","tid":1427794,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家將行動散發出去<br />\n繼續unlike,罷買，罷訂，罷找數！！！！！<br />\n唔容許玩具界有呢粒老鼠屎"},{"pid":"0807e8e6197616e6c96b10b20c4b16530dad9083","tid":1427794,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"推撚到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5da99ac29221f7d07596e13c871cf1d696f6852","tid":1427794,"uid":90392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bc83b0de65d115aeda17a46b98a7bd88b4dcc86f","tid":1427794,"uid":31961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"未爆呢單野之前落左二千幾訂點撚樣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5fadc7f5b7efca8353b692b8b397eca33a2b15","tid":1427794,"uid":159577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"上星期仲買左隻figma, 正仆街"},{"pid":"8854ab6bad4b15063497289befd8707daeedb849","tid":1427794,"uid":104400,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"你撕左張單佢咪又係會放返出舖賣<br />\n香港人金魚記憶,轉個頭就唔記得左,永遠都會有豬貪平<br />\n你咁樣變相俾佢賺左你個訂金"},{"pid":"9f0dabc1fa7f95b013f5499ab1f9664dc69d78cd","tid":1427794,"uid":9950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"未訂過 但再唔會訂"},{"pid":"46224e8a4deaf835d0b4649a9106debc7a3ac6e9","tid":1427794,"uid":10509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"以後會叫朋友唔好去依間買<br />\n以為FB 講幾句件事就完?<br />\n要你全線執呀 屌你老母藍絲撐警老闆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫你班廢老白衣人去買日本玩具啦柒頭"},{"pid":"f2bc753ba2b320cd798ac004b166906fd4a9c89f","tid":1427794,"uid":112316,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"咪撚撕<br />\n第一，比人食訂<br />\n第二，件貨炒起佢又賺一筆<br />\n今日開始唔去精品消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289db88530c675885bbabd057db295c94172564b","tid":1427794,"uid":266968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"撕左咪益左訂比佢？ 叫佢老母退訂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個再幫趁精品，就等